20
00:04:33,485 --> 00:04:35,443
I'm 15 1/2.

21
00:04:58,199 --> 00:05:00,699
It's the crossing
of the river.

22
00:05:00,742 --> 00:05:03,450
When I go back to Saigon...

23
00:05:03,491 --> 00:05:05,742
