I'm on a journey...

24
00:05:05,784 --> 00:05:08,284
especially
when I take the bus.

25
00:05:08,285 --> 00:05:11,744
That day, it's the end
of the school holidays.

26
00:05:11,786 --> 00:05:14,411
I don't remember which one.

27
00:05:14,454 --> 00:05:17,287
I went to spend it in Sa-Dec
with my two brothers...

28
00:05:17,287 --> 00:05:19,911
