Because that's the way it is.

34
00:06:16,468 --> 00:06:17,801
I wish you'd die.

35
00:07:33,278 --> 00:07:34,654
Paul?

36
00:07:39,113 --> 00:07:40,405
Paulo?

37
00:07:46,782 --> 00:07:48,782
Paul, come to bed.

38
00:07:50,908 --> 00:07:53,491
You mustn't be afraid
anymore:

39
