83
00:12:14,723 --> 00:12:17,014
No native woman, either.

84
00:12:17,098 --> 00:12:19,848
That hat, I never leave it.

85
00:12:19,931 --> 00:12:22,848
I have that, this hat.

86
00:12:22,891 --> 00:12:25,849
