makes me whole.

87
00:12:25,850 --> 00:12:27,975
I'm never without it.

88
00:13:35,326 --> 00:13:36,825
So it's the crossing...

89
00:13:36,867 --> 00:13:39,076
of one of the branches
of the Mekong...

90
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:42,869
on the ferry that's between
Vinh Long and Sa-Dec...

91
00:13:42,869 --> 00:13:46,285
in the great plains
of mud and rice...

92
00:13:46,328 --> 00:13:48,370
of southern Indochina...

93
00:13:48,371 --> 00:13:50,371
the plain of the birds.

94
00:15:32,062 --> 00:15:35,187
Excuse me, mademoiselle.
Do you smoke?

95
00:15:38,064 --> 00:15:39,397
No, thank you.

96
00:16:01,070 --> 00:16:02,611
