104
00:16:46,956 --> 00:16:50,372
-I live in Vinh Long.
-Where in Vinh Long?

105
00:16:50,373 --> 00:16:54,749
On the river just outside.
The big house with the terraces.

106
00:16:54,749 --> 00:16:56,875
The blue stone one?

107
00:16:56,917 --> 00:16:58,333
Yes.

108
00:16:58,375 --> 00:17:00,417
It's a Chinese house.

109
00:17:00,501 --> 00:17:02,876
I am Chinese.

110
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:05,918
Chinese.

111
00:17:06,002 --> 00:17:08,877
He's from
that financial minority...

112
00:17:08,878 --> 00:17:11,586
