162
00:21:30,775 --> 00:21:32,733
Do you know the coupole?

163
00:21:32,776 --> 00:21:34,401
I went to France once.

164
00:21:34,442 --> 00:21:37,234
It was in the north,
near the Belgian border.

165
00:21:37,277 --> 00:21:39,943
I only know here--
the Mekong, Saigon.

166
00:21:39,986 --> 00:21:41,069
You like Saigon?

167
00:21:41,111 --> 00:21:43,486
Yes, I like Saigon.

168
00:21:43,529 --> 00:21:46,903
I like Saigon, too.
Cholon above all.

169
00:21:46,946 --> 00:21:49,488
Cholon, it's like China.

170
00:24:57,117 --> 00:24:59,784
That's it. It's here.

171
00:25:43,378 --> 00:25:44,628
Good-bye.

172
00:26:34,016 --> 00:26:36,974
