like that?

191
00:27:25,196 --> 00:27:27,821
Anybody,
people walking by.

192
00:27:30,113 --> 00:27:32,363
It's always appealed to me.

193
00:27:32,406 --> 00:27:33,614
What?

194
00:27:34,698 --> 00:27:37,114
