in the afternoon...

230
00:34:25,631 --> 00:34:27,798
the time of the siesta.

231
00:34:27,799 --> 00:34:29,799
It's in Cholon...

232
00:34:29,799 --> 00:34:32,298
in the alleyways of Cholon...

233
00:34:32,299 --> 00:34:34,967
in the smell of soup,
roast meat...

234
00:34:34,968 --> 00:34:38,300
